attendant-uniforms-evolution-then-and-now-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappearance%20standards%20throughout%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20jet%20age%20to%20the%20mid-1990s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20airlines%20said%20this%20lured%20in%20high-paying%20travelers%20and%20created%20an%20elevated%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStewardesses%2C%20as%20they%20were%20called%20then%2C%20couldn't%20be%20too%20tall%20or%20too%20short%2C%20too%20old%20or%20too%20young.%20They%20couldn't%20be%20heavy-set%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20had%20to%20be%20unmarried%20and%20childless.%20In%20the%201970s%2C%20Southwest%20Airlines%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-airlines-history-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitted%20its%20flight%20attendants%20in%20hot%20pants%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gogo%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20the%20aviation%20industry%20has%20since%20shifted%20to%20focus%20its%20flight%20attendants%20more%20narrowly%20on%20safety%20and%20service.%20With%20that%20still%20come%20appearance%20standards%20like%20skirt%20and%20nail%20length%2C%20wearing%20a%20tie%2C%20and%20hair%20style%20rules%2C%20but%20they%20are%20far%20less%20demanding%20compared%20to%20past%20eras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Western%20carriers%20today%20allow%20female%20cabin%20crew%20to%20wear%20tennis%20shoes%20instead%20of%20heels%2C%20or%20pants%20instead%20of%20skirts%20and%20dresses.%20Most%20can%20also%20choose%20to%20wear%20minimal%20or%20no%20makeup%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falaska-creates-gender-neutral-uniforms-for-flight-attendants-airport-staff-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20airlines%20allow%20men%20to%20wear%20stud%20earrings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20carriers%20have%20yet%20to%20ditch%20the%20traditional%20appearance%20expectations%20and%20maintain%20more%20conservative%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20Airways%20is%20known%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20having%20strict%20codes%20of%20appearance%20and%20other%20things%2C%20likely%20an%20effort%20to%20maintain%20its%20luxury-focused%20brand%20and%20professionalism.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-airlines-in-the-world-skytrax-survey-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairline%2C%20with%20its%20exacting%20standards%2C%20has%20been%20rated%20the%20world's%20best%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20says%20the%20strict%20rules%20haven't%20deterred%20cabin%20crew%20applications%3A%20A%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20only%206%25%20to%208%25%20of%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20applicants%20are%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20with%20Qatar%20flight%20attendants%20Daina%20Haughton%20and%20Milan%20Rankovic%20and%20style%20specialist%20Kristine%20Odejar%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20airline's%20appearance%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221afe3cfc-f11e-43e8-9727-567470daeb4d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMakeup%2C%20skin%2C%20and%20nail%20requirements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaughton%20said%20Qatar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeaths-on-flights-passengers-cabin-crew-training-handle-dead-bodies-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflight%20attendants%3C%2Fa%3E%20learn%20how%20to%20do%20their%20hair%20and%20makeup%20in%20initial%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20involves%20working%20with%20%26quot%3Bgrooming%20officers%26quot%3B%20like%20Odejar%2C%20who%20help%20match%20flight%20attendants'%20makeup%20to%20their%20skin%20tone%20and%20texture%20and%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20apply%20it%20best%20using%20different%20brushes%20and%20pens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaughton%20said%20the%20training%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bhard%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20consultants%20provided%20tips%20that%20cabin%20crew%20%26quot%3Bcan%20do%20to%20correct%20certain%20things%20that%20you%20wouldn't%20just%20know.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%20that%20she%20spends%20two%20hours%20getting%20ready%20for%20flights%2C%20setting%20aside%20one%20hour%20for%20hair%20and%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20training%20session%20observed%20by%20BI%2C%20Odejar%20explained%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20basic%20makeup%20items%20required%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoured-singapores-flight-attendant-training-center-looked-physically-demanding-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efemale%20cabin%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20they%20need%20%26quot%3Bfull%20coverage%26quot%3B%20foundation%20and%20concealer%2C%20black%20mascara%20that%20isn't%20%26quot%3Btoo%20clumpy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20matte%20or%20sheen%20blush%20(no%20glitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221077%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Qatar%20flight%20attendant%20putting%20on%20lipstick%20in%20the%20mirror.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68016e3fa466d2b74ab384f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQatar%20Airways%20has%20strict%20beauty%20rules%20that%20cabin%20crew%20must%20follow%20when%20flying.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELipstick%20and%20nail%20colors%20can%20be%20deep%20pink%2C%20deep%20red%2C%20or%20burgundy%2C%20while%20nail%20polish%20options%20also%20include%20nude%2C%20clear%2C%20or%20French.%20The%20burgundy%20theme%20is%20in%20line%20with%20Qatar's%20brand%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOdejar%20gives%20tips%20like%20using%20long-lasting%20concealer%20because%20it's%20%26quot%3Bbulletproof%26quot%3B%20and%20won't%20come%20off%20the%20face%2C%20and%20using%20powder%20to%20set%20the%20makeup.%20She%20also%20said%20to%20prioritize%20skin%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20also%20does%20not%20allow%20visible%20tattoos%2C%20a%20common%20guideline%20across%20most%20global%20airlines.%20However%2C%20some%20carriers%20like%20Virgin%20Atlantic%20Airways%20have%20become%20more%20lenient%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-atlantic-gender-neutral-uniform-policy-flight-attendants-pilots-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallow%20tattoos%20of%20various%20sizes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e55c685-1e73-4509-8f62-b7ef5635b3a8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrict%20hairstyles%20and%20clean%20mustaches%20for%20men%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaughton%20said%20the%20acceptable%20hairstyle%20for%20women%20is%20a%20bun%20situated%20low%20enough%20so%20that%20the%20uniform%20hat%20can%20fit%20over%20it.%20She%20added%20that%20hair%20can't%20be%20too%20oily%20and%20must%20be%20a%20natural%20color%20if%20dyed%3B%20no%20rainbow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20cabin%20crew%20must%20use%20hair%20nets%20to%20cover%20the%20bun%2C%20and%20they%20can%20choose%20to%20use%20one%20or%20two%20scrunchies%3B%20Haughton%20prefers%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOdejar%20described%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-flight-attendants-uniforms-gender-neutral-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrooming%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20men's%20hair%2C%20which%20include%20properly%20styling%20it%20and%20using%20grooming%20wax%20or%20clay%20to%20make%20it%20look%20neat%20and%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20basically%20just%20need%20to%20apply%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20product%20so%20it%20doesn't%20look%20over-gelled%20or%20having%20that%20kind%20of%20wet%20look%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221477%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Haughton%20demonstrating%20her%20hair%20routine%20and%20putting%20on%20the%20uniform%20hat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680166c3c6ad288d147e80cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221108%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlight%20attendant%20Daina%20Haughton%20demonstrates%20her%20hair%20routine.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERankovic%20said%20male%20cabin%20crew%20can%20have%20facial%20hair%2C%20but%20only%20mustaches%2C%20not%20beards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20mustache%20needs%20to%20be%20neatly%20shaven%2C%20cannot%20grow%20over%20the%20upper%20lip%20or%20below%20the%20lip%20line%2C%20and%20must%20be%20grown%20out%20by%20the%20time%20a%20trip%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20you%20need%20to%20show%20up%20for%20the%20flights%20with%20%5Ba%5D%20fully%20grown%20mustache%2C%26quot%3B%20Rankovic%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20need%20to%20do%20it%20on%20your%20days%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20face%20must%20be%20clearly%20shaven%3B%20no%205%20o'clock%20shadows.%20The%20beard%20ban%20helps%20maintain%20a%20clean%20and%20professional%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20told%20the%20Daily%20Telegraph%20in%20December%20that%20gray%20hair%20is%20also%20not%20allowed%2C%20and%20bald%20spots%20must%20be%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232ee903d-05a1-44cd-ab22-ce7690dc42a5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUniforms%20must%20be%20neat%20and%20exact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQatar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendant-best-and-worst-things-about-job-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflight%20attendants%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20provided%20with%20specific%20uniforms%2C%20including%20skirts%2C%20pants%2C%20blazers%2C%20and%20plain%20socks%20with%20no%20logos%20or%20designs.%20Women%20wear%20hats%2C%20and%20men%20wear%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20crew%20member%20must%20carry%20a%20spare%20uniform%20in%20case%20of%20spills%20or%20other%20messes%20during%20the%20flight.%20They%20also%20have%20a%20separate%20winter%20jacket%20when%20traveling%20to%20colder%20climates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Qatar%20grooming%20instructor%20said%20the%20only%20men's%20accessory%20allowed%20is%20a%20watch%2C%20while%20women's%20jewe