%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretail-investors-trump-trade-war-stock-market-panic-bitcoin-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20investing%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20but%20she's%20been%20discouraged%20by%20the%20market%20volatility%20and%20has%20decided%20to%20wait%20until%20things%20calm%20down%20before%20buying%20in.%20The%20possibility%20of%20investing%20money%20into%20the%20market%20and%20immediately%20seeing%20it%20shrink%20after%20another%20tariff%20negotiation%20triggers%20a%20sell-off%20is%20unappealing%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20I%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20because%20it's%20time%20to%20diversify%20my%20assets%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20grow%20my%20money%20so%20I%20have%20a%20better%20future%20later%20on%2C%20but%20with%20the%20way%20that%20everything%20is%20shifting%20right%20now%2C%20I%20get%20anxiety%20reading%20the%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Jauregui%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20payroll%20specialist%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarry%20Woodland%20started%20investing%20in%20stocks%20during%20the%20week%20of%20April%207%2C%20just%20as%20tariff%20news%20was%20swinging%20the%20market%20wildly.%20He%20began%20by%20buying%20ETFs%20tracking%20the%20global%20stock%20market%20and%20individual%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-alphabet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphabet%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgoogl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOOGL%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENVDA%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20actually%20investing%20a%20little%20bit%20after%20the