u%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20save%20up%20your%20cash%20and%20wait%20until%20you%20have%20a%20larger%20sum%20to%20invest%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20necessary%20and%20might%20actually%20be%20suboptimal.%20It's%20hard%20to%20time%20the%20market%20correctly%20and%20enter%20at%20the%20right%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20systematically%20buying%20every%20paycheck%2C%20then%20sometimes%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20buying%20at%20the%20absolute%20cheapest%20point%2C%20sometimes%20at%20a%20medium%20point%2C%20and%20sometimes%20at%20a%20more%20expensive%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Klingensmith%20said.%20It's%20OK%20to%20not%20buy%20in%20at%20the%20low%20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20dollar%20cost%20averaging%20helps%20investors%20smooth%20out%20the%20cost%20of%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e59fc73-fcb5-4af5-b70f-db9e188eb59a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStart%20simple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20your%20first%20foray%20into%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20stick%20with%20the%20basics%2C%20like%20index%20funds%2C%20ETFs%2C%20and%20blue-chip%20stocks%2C%20Klingensmith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20with%20a%20longer%20investing%20horizon%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20have%20a%20higher%20risk%20tolerance%20as%20there's%20more%20time%20to%20weather%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20the%20market.%20Younger%20investors%20can%20often%20put%20up%20to%20100%25%20of%20their%20portfolio%20into%20equities%20and%20gradually%20dial%20down%20the%20risk%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodland's%20applying%20this%20mindset%20to%20his%20investing%20strategy%20and%20taking%20some%20risks%20on%20individual%20stocks%20while%20he's%20young.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Tech%20stuff%20in%20my%20portfolio%20does%20worry%20me%20a%20bit%2C%20but%20it's%20offset%20by%20my%20recovery%20period.%20I've%20got%20a%20long%20time%20to%20invest%2C%26quot%3B%20Woodland%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteer%20clear%20of%20the%20more%20complicated%20investment%20vehicles%20though%2C%20Klingensmith%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20people%20are%20talking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-investing-bonanza-new-etf-retail-investors-apollo-spdr-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20private%20debt%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investment-strategies-help-build-wealth-financial-independence-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Klingensmith%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20tend%20to%20be%20for%20the%20smaller%20investor%20because%20at%20least%20at%20this%20point%2C%20those%20investments%20are%20hard%20to%20get%20into%20and%20out%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExamples%20of%20index%20funds%20that%20provide%20broad%20exposure%20to%20the%20market%20include%20the%20SPDR%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fspdr-sp-500-etf-us78462f1030%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESPY%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20Vanguard%20Total%20World%20Stock%20Index%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-total-world-stock-index-fund-etf-shares-us9220427424%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVT%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20the%20iShares%20MSCI%20World%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-msci-world-etf-us4642863926%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EURTH%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac96569f-4ccb-417d-bb9a-d1f350a05419%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20diversified%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20diversified%20sounds%20deceptively%20simple%2C%20but%20it's%20often%20hard%20to%20heed%20this%20tip%20when%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20doing%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20started%20investing%20last%20year%2C%20you%20might%20have%20been%20tempted%20to%20allocate%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20your%20portfolio%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-funds-top-stock-picks-magnificent-7-tesla-trump-trade-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMagnificent%20Seven%3C%2Fa%3E%20stocks%20due%20to%20their%20stellar%20performance.%20Now%2C%20you%20might%20be%20wishing%20that%20you%20had%20more%20exposure%20to%20the%20utilities%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20exciting%20to%20invest%20thematically%2C%20such%20as%20betting%20big%20on%20the%20AI%20trend%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20best%20foundation%20to%20base%20your%20portfolio%20on%2C%20according%20to%20Klingensmith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20winners%20within%20the%20stock%20market%20change.%20Five%20years%20ago%20nobody%20would%20have%20dreamed%20that%20AI%20would%20have%20been%20this%20much%20of%20a%20leader%20in%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Klingensmith%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20purchasing%20a%20broad%20basket%20of%20securities%2C%20you're%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20some%20winners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20institutional%20and%20retail%20investors%20had%20been%20betting%20on%20US%20exceptionalism%20fueling%20stocks%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20but%20the%20trade%20war%20has%20proven%20that%20the%20strategy%20isn't%20watertight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20tariffs%2C%20I%20would%20have%20invested%20my%20money%20into%20an%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20fund%2C%20but%20I've%20actually%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20the%20Invesco%20FTSE%20All%20World%20fund%2C%20mainly%20because%20I%20don't%20really%20feel%20comfortable%20in%20investing%20wholly%20in%20US%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Woodland%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20understand%20that%20the%20All%20World%20fund%20is%20around%2060%25%20US%20stocks.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20sleep%20better%20at%20night%20knowing%20that%20there%20is%20the%20insurance%20of%20having%20international%20exposure%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231203a0e-cc23-4258-994c-a07e9b126488%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20honest%20with%20yourself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20start%20investing%2C%20you%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20your%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20financial%20goals%2C%20and%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20investing%20is%20an%20inherently%20emotional%20experience%2C%20Klingensmith%20cautions.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20say%20enough%20that%20all%20of%20us%2C%20myself%20absolutely%20included%2C%20are%20emotional%20at%20times%20like%20this%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20want%20to%20sell%20investments%20because%20they've%20gone%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20advice%3F%20Don't%20go%20for%20more%20risky%20investments%20if%20you%20know%20you%20can't%20handle%20the%20stress.%20Define%20your%20financial%20goals%20and%20time%20horizon%2C%20and%20keep%20a%20long-term%20mindset%20by%20avoiding%20checking%20on%20your%20portfolio%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlingensmith%20added%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20bad%20idea%20to%20derisk%20your%20portfolio%20and%20hold%20more%20cash%20at%20times.%20Especially%20during%20an%20economic%20downturn%2C%20keeping%20cash%20on%20hand%20for%20easy%20access%20can%20be%20more%20valuable%20than%20investing%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20OK%20to%20focus%20on%20that%20cash%20cushion%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20just%20given%20the%20amount%20of%20uncertainty%20that's%20everywhere%2C%20not%20just%20in%20financial%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Klingensmith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-tips-how-to-start-investing-trade-war-trump-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745054401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68027eecc6ad288d147e9243%3Fformat%3Djpeg%