%20data%20center%20since%20Nvidia's%2010-year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famd-lisa-su-ceo-nvidia-competition-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehead%20start.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20at%20the%20edge%3F%20The%20field%20is%20more%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20Papermaster%20what%20he%20thinks%20the%20future%20of%20handheld%20AI%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20Q%26amp%3BA%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20most%20prominent%20use%20for%20AI%20computing%20in%20edge%20devices%20like%20laptops%20and%20phones%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20case%20you're%20starting%20to%20see%20is%20local%2C%20immediate%2C%20low-latency%20content%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20do%20we%20use%20PCs%3F%20We%20use%20them%20to%20communicate%2C%20and%20we%20use%20them%20to%20create%20content.%20As%20you%20and%20I%20are%20talking%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20a%20Microsoft%20Teams%20event%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20is%20running%20underneath%20this.%20I%20could%20have%20a%20correction%20on%20it%20such%20that%20if%20I%20look%20side%20to%20side%2C%20you%20just%20see%20me%20centered.%20That's%20an%20option.%20I%20can%20hit%20automatic%20translation%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20be%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20not%20speak%20any%20English%2C%20and%20we%20could%20have%20simultaneous%20translation%20once%20these%20things%20become%20truly%20embedded%20and%20operational%2C%20which%20is%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20truly%20amazing%20what's%20coming%20because%20just%20locally%20on%20your%20PC%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20verbally%20describe%3A%20'Hey%2C%20I'm%20building%20a%20PowerPoint.%20I%20need%20this.%20I%20need%20these%20features.%20I'm%20running%20Adobe.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20want.'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I've%20got%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20cloud.%20I've%20got%20to%20run%20the%20big%2C%20heavy%20compute.%20It's%20more%20expensive%20and%20it%20takes%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20immediate%20example%20that's%20front%20and%20center%2C%20and%20this%20is%20why%20we've%20invested%20heavily%20in%20AI%20PCs.%20That's%20imminent%20from%20Microsoft%20and%20others%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20application%20that%20we're%20already%20seeing%20is%20autonomous%20anything.%20It%20starts%20with%20cars%2C%20but%20it's%20way%20beyond%20cars.%20It's%20the%20autonomous%20factory%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOK%2C%20say%20it's%202030%20%E2%80%94%20how%20much%20inference%20is%20done%20at%20the%20edge%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20it'll%20be%20a%20majority.%20I%20can't%20say%20when%20the%20switch%20over%20is%20because%20it's%20driven%20by%20the%20applications%20%E2%80%94%20the%20development%20of%20the%20killer%20apps%20that%20can%20run%20on%20edge%20devices.%20We're%20just%20seeing%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20spear%20now%2C%20but%20I%20think%20this%20moves%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20consider%20phones%20as%20an%20analogy.%20Those%20phones%20were%20just%20a%20nice%20assist%20until%20the%20App%20Store%20came%20out%20and%20made%20it%20really%20easy%20to%20create%20a%20ton%20of%20applications%20on%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20things%20that%20used%20to%20always%20be%20done%20with%20more%20performant%20computing%20could%20be%20done%20more%20locally.%20Things%20that%20were%20done%20in%20the%20cloud%20could%20be%20done%20locally.%20As%20we%20start%20to%20get%20killer%20applications%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20start%20to%20see%20that%20shift%20go%20very%20rapidly.%20So%20it's%20in%20the%20next%20three%20to%20six%20years%2C%20no%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20keep%20running%20into%20examples%20that%20suggest%20the%20way%20models%20are%20getting%20better%20is%20to%20just%20keep%20piling%20on%20more%20inference%20compute.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20know%20that%20three%20years%20from%20now%2C%20there's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20some%20breakthrough%20that%20makes%20all%20these%20devices%20being%20designed%20now%20completely%20out%20of%20date%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20you're%20describing%20is%20to%20gain%20even%20more%20capability%20and%20accuracy.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20what%20we%20have%20is%20not%20useful.%20It's%20just%20going%20to%20be%20constantly%20improving%2C%20and%20the%20improvement%20goes%20into%20two%20vectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20vector%20is%20becoming%20more%20accurate.%20It%20can%20do%20more%20things%2C%20and%20typically%20drives%20more%20compute.%20There's%20an%20equal%20vector%20that%20runs%20in%20parallel%2C%20saying%2C%20'How%20could%20I%20be%20more%20optimized%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20call%20it%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexplaining-deepseek-chinese-models-efficiency-scaring-markets-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%20moment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20sort%20of%20shook%20the%20world.%20Now%20you%20have%20everybody%20%E2%80%94%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20making%20their%20models%20more%20efficient.%20So%20you%20have%20both%20examples%20where%20it's%20taking%20more%20and%20more%20compute%20and%20examples%20where%20there's%20innovation%20driving%20more%20and%20more%20efficiency.%20That's%20not%20going%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-workloads-transition-inference-amd-mark-papermaster-edge-devices-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745053202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68013897a466d2b74ab378a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-workloads-transition-inference-amd-mark-papermaster-edge-devices-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AMD%20plans%20to%20capitalize%20on%20AI%20inference%20workloads%20moving%20to%20edge%20devices%2C%20CTO