ig%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20players%20are%20all%20investing%20heavily%20in%20quantum%20advancement%2C%20hoping%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20IBM%20%E2%80%94%20a%20longtime%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20field%2C%20with%20several%20different%20prototype%20chips%20and%20its%20circuit-based%20commercial%20quantum%20computer%2C%20IBM%20Quantum%20System%20One%2C%20which%20was%20unveiled%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20announced%20its%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOcelot%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20February.%20The%20company%20says%20it%C2%A0represents%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20error%20correction%20and%20scalability%2C%20two%20key%20issues%20that%20have%20long%20slowed%20advancement%20in%20the%20field.%20Its%20announcement%20came%20just%20a%20week%20after%20Microsoft%20debuted%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMajorana%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20only%20a%20few%20months%20after%20Google's%20Willow%20chip%20hit%20the%20scene%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20also%20aiming%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20action.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20at%20GTC%20that%20it%20is%20developing%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmajor-quantum-computing-announcements-made-during-nvidias-gtc-conference-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20research%20lab%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258cd583d-5bcc-4081-add5-96dbf0fa0b8a%5C%22%3EThe%20government%20is%20betting%20on%20quantum%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Defense%20Advanced%20Research%20Projects%20Agency%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20research%20and%20development%20agency%2C%20has%20expanded%20its%20Quantum%20Benchmarking%20Initiative%20this%20year%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20achieve%20utility-scale%20operation%20by%202033.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDARPA%20in%20early%20April%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.darpa.mil%2Fnews%2F2025%2Fcompanies-targeting-quantum-computers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20had%20chosen%2018%20companies%20to%20test%20and%20advance%20various%20technologies%20for%20creating%20qubits%20%E2%80%94%20the%20building%20block%20for%20quantum%20computers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20superconducting%20qubits%2C%20trapped%20ion%20qubits%2C%20and%20other%20novel%20approaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20and%20PsiQuantum%20have%20already%20advanced%20to%20the%20third%20and%20final%20phase%20of%20DARPA's%20quantum%20initiative.%20IBM%2C%20IonQ%2C%20and%20Rigetti%20Computing%20are%20among%20the%20newest%20companies%20joining%20the%20QBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241bd2a90-ca41-4610-ad22-bde1f4b81e43%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20quantum%20supercomputer%20is%20nearly%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIBM%20plans%20to%20debut%20the%20world's%20first%20quantum-centric%20supercomputer%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20system%20will%20use%20the%20modular%20IBM%20Quantum%20System%20Two%20architecture%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20scalable%20and%20upgradeable.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20feature%20over%204%2C000%20qubits%20and%20aims%20to%20break%20existing%20records%20in%20the%20field%2C%20eventually%20surpassing%20the%20size%20of%20the%20largest%20quantum%20computer%20by%20more%20than%20threefold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIBM%20CEO%20Arvind%20Krishna%20told%C2%A0Time%C2%A0in%20March%20that%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20remarkable%26quot%3B%20is%20on%20the%20horizon%20for%20quantum%20technology%20and%20that%20the%20company%20has%20positioned%20itself%20to%20create%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20foundational%20technology%20through%20advancements%20in%20quantum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a3d80be-e17a-4a91-8dbd-ef436ca457da%5C%22%3EAdvancement%20comes%20with%20security%20risks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we're%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20quantum%20revolution%2C%20cybersecurity%20professionals%20have%20previously%20warned%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20tech%20comes%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20own%20risks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20basic%20data%20privacy%20or%20the%20chance%20of%20personal%20financial%20details%20becoming%20public.%20From%20national%20security%20secrets%20to%20the%20blockchain%20and%20beyond%2C%20all%20encrypted%20data%20will%20be%20readily%20accessible%20and%2C%20more%20worryingly%2C%20manipulatable%20by%20anyone%20with%20a%20fully%20fault-tolerant%20and%20quantum-capable%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarl%20Holmqvist%20has%20served%20as%20a%20quantum%20security%20advisor%20to%20major%20government%20bodies%2C%20including%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20and%20NATO.%20He%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Lastwall%2C%20which%20provides%20cybersecurity%20solutions%20designed%20to%20protect%20users%20from%20quantum%20computing%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20peeling%20back%20the%20layers%2C%20it's%20like%20anything%20that's%20internet-connected%20will%20likely%20have%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Holmqvist%20previously%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20we%20trust%20that%20the%20links%20between%20systems%20are%20secure%20and%20the%20data%20that's%20gone%20between%20them%20is%20secure%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20get%20into%20those%20that%20they're%20encrypted.%20If%20you%20take%20away%20that%20default%20assumption%2C%20it%20allows%20so%20many%20new%20entry%20points%20into%20systems%20that%20it%20becomes%20quite%20concerning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e53d1add-e993-435d-825c-864b4e61ee43%5C%22%3EHiring%20managers%20are%20starting%20to%20take%20notice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20shows%20that%20the%20salary%20bands%20for%20jobs%20in%20quantum%20computing%20range%20from%20%24150%2C000%20on%20the%20low%20end%20to%20well%20past%20%24500%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20role%20and%20company.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdirector-sap-labs-explains-qualifications-culture-quantum-computing-field-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHiring%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdirector-sap-labs-explains-qualifications-culture-quantum-computing-field-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20managers%20are%20paying%20attention%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYaad%20Oren%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20SAP%20Labs%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20software%20companies%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20recruiters%20in%20the%20field%20look%20for%20curiosity%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20we%20need%20expertise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20quantum%20is%20a%20very%20deep%20science%20and%20practice%20that%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20you%20follow%20the%20industry%2C%20you%20see%20there%20are%20also%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-say-major-quantum-computing-breakthroughs-are-years-away-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edisruptions%20going%20with%20quantum%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Oren%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20definitely%20looking%20for%20change%20agents%20and%20curiosity%20is%20needed%20because%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20not%20sure%20at%20all%20that%20the%20current%20quantum%20technology%20we%20have%20now%20will%20be%20the%20winning%20architecture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20building%20a%20building%20from%20the%20ground%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-officially-entered-quantum-era-major-advancements-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745051581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F618294e4326b260018349628%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-officially-entered-quantum-era-major-advancements-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Major%20advancements%20in%20tech%20and%20science%20are%20brewing%20as%20the%20industry%20makes%20its%20way%20through%20the%20'International%20Year%20of%20Quantum.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-officially-entered-quantum-era-major-advancements-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20to%20Raise%20a%20Little%20Nature%20Lover%3F%20Start%20With%20These%2010%20Thoughtful%20Gifts%20(That%20Aren%E2%80%99t%20Toys!)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-yoast-seo-table-of-contents%5C%22%3E%3Ch2%3EQuick%20Peek%3A%2010%20Non-Toy%20Gifts%20For%20Kids%20Who%20Love%20Nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F421275%2Fthoughtful-gifts-for-children-make-them-nature-lovers%2F%23h-1-a-grow-your-own-garden-kit%5C%22%20data-level%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E1.%20A%20grow-your-own-garden%20kit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F421275%2Fthoughtful-gifts-for-children-make-them-nature-lovers%2F%23h-2-their-own-tree-yes-really%5C%22%20data-level%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E2.%20Their%20own%20tree%20(yes%2C%20really!)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F421275%2Fthoughtful-gifts-for-children-make-them-nature-lovers%2F%23h-3-a-nature-explorer-s-journal%5C%22%20data-level%3D%5