0Minnesota%20native%20felt%20trapped%20in%20her%20air-conditioned%20home%20for%20months%20at%20a%20time.%20She%20worried%20things%20would%20only%20get%20worse%20as%20climate%20change%20takes%20its%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fall%20quit%20happening%20because%20it%20went%20from%20drought%20summers%20to%20dead-looking%20leaves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2066-year-old%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20both%20retired%2C%20were%20also%20eager%20to%20live%20in%20a%20small%2C%20walkable%20city%20in%20a%20blue%20state%20with%20affordable%20home%20prices%2C%20good%20healthcare%2C%20and%20legal%20marijuana%2C%20which%20Center%20uses%20to%20help%20treat%20her%20chronic%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202023%2C%20the%20couple%20sold%20their%20Benton%20home%20for%20%24195%2C000%2C%20uprooted%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20moved%20to%20Lansing%2C%20Michigan%2C%20where%20they%20bought%20an%20old%20home%20for%20%2465%2C000%20that%20they're%20fixing%20up%20themselves.%20They%20live%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20the%20state%20capitol%2C%20biking%20and%20walking%20trails%2C%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20a%20ballpark.%20Lansing%20hits%20the%20%26quot%3Bsweet%20spot%26quot%3B%20for%20affordability%20and%20climate%2C%20Center%20said%2C%20though%20they%20left%20their%20community%20behind%20in%20Arkansas.%20They%20didn't%20know%20anyone%20in%20Lansing%20when%20they%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECenter's%20move%20is%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20trend.%20The%20data%20shows%20that%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20domestic%20migration%20to%20the%20Sunbelt%20has%20slowed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-north-midwestern-snowbelt-becoming-new-sunbelt-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflyover%20country%20is%20becoming%20the%20new%20place%20to%20be%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20prices%20and%20rents%20have%20risen%20dramatically%20in%20many%20Southern%20and%20Sunbelt%20communities%2C%20particularly%20as%20