d%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScB-4a6dV6jak2g6t-CoOdxFIENDSZggxHVbvsz6ry4dGoUjg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20by%20Gusto%2C%20a%20small-business%20payment%20and%20HR%20platform%2C%20found%20that%20since%202022%2C%20the%20number%20of%20workers%2080%20and%20older%20has%20increased%20by%20about%2025%25%2C%20compared%20to%204%25%20growth%20in%20the%20overall%20workforce.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20that%20number%20represents%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20workforce%20%E2%80%94%20about%20one%20in%201%2C000%20US%20workers.%20The%20analysis%20was%20based%20on%20payroll%20records%20from%20over%20400%2C000%20small%20business%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20and%20current%20prices%20are%20in%20a%20place%20where%20they're%20really%20forcing%20folks%20to%20reconsider%20or%20even%20rejoin%20the%20labor%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Nich%20Tremper%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Gusto%2C%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20folks%20who%20are%20just%20likely%20looking%20to%20earn%20a%20little%20bit%20extra%20to%20have%20their%20money%20last%20as%20long%20as%20the%20month%20does.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c23f51b-986f-4978-9a6a-1da020e1c633%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavigating%20work%20amid%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20workers%20in%20their%2080s%20and%20older%2C%20including%20Uhrinyak%2C%20said%20they've%20taken%20on%20new%20jobs%20amid%20health%20issues%2C%20as%20they%20had%20few%20other%20options%20to%20stay%20afloat%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Uhrinyak%20resigned%20from%20his%20role%20as%20a%20construction%20coordinator%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmounjaro-vs-ozempic-side-effects-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20effects%20he%20experienced%20from%20taking%20Ozempic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20working%20with%20his%20son