0She%20told%20BI%20that%20many%20older%20workers%20approaching%20or%20past%20retirement%20age%20have%20had%20to%20take%20blue-collar%20jobs%20that%20are%20lower-paying%20and%20riskier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20slightly%20less%20dangerous%20jobs%20for%20older%20workers%20than%20for%20prime-age%20workers%2C%20but%20the%20dangers%20that%20they%20face%20are%20much%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Morrissey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiane%20Knaus%2C%2082%2C%20broke%20her%20ankle%20in%20September%2C%20and%20she%20temporarily%20stopped%20working%20as%20a%20freelance%20writer%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20recovery.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20with%20limited%20income%2C%20Knaus%20said%20she%20began%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20generate%20some%20additional%20cash.%20She's%20about%20to%20start%20a%20desk%20job%20for%20a%20trucking%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20on%20my%20Social%20Security%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Knaus%2C%20who%20lives%20near%20Annapolis%2C%20Maryland.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20taking%20life%20year%20by%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2212f1fadb-47f3-4025-9f5b-f6ef647d0649%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20tough%20job%20market%20for%20older%20Americans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20workers%20in%20their%2060s%20and%20older%20told%20BI%20this%20year%20that%20finding%20a%20well-paying%20job%20feels%20nearly%20impossible%20amid%20a%20tight%20job%20market%20and%20reduced%20white-collar%20hiring.%20It's%20leading%20many%20to%20seek%20blue-collar%20roles%20and%20other%20part-time%20positions%20that%20pay%20a%20bit%20more%20than%20minimum%20wage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPamela%20Levier%2C%2081%2C%20recently%20resigned%20from%20her%20full-time%20service%20department%20job%20at%20the%20car%20dealership%20where%20she'd%20worked%20since%202013.%20While%20she%20has%20four%20pensions%20tied%20to%20her%20and%20her%20late%20husband%2C%20she%20said%20they're%20%26quot%3Bnot%20large%20amounts%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she's%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pamala%20Levier%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802789cc6ad288d147e90a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPamala%20Levier%20said%20she%20doesn't%20have%20enough%20in%20savings%20to%20stop%20working.%3Cp%3EPamala%20Levier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dealership%20was%20sold%2C%20and%20the%20new%20owner%20was%20expected%20to%20make%20changes%20that%20Levier%20felt%20would%20negatively%20affect%20her%20work%20experience%20and%20could%20put%20her%20job%20at%20risk.%20She%20said%20she's%20been%20looking%20for%20positions%20at%20other%20car%20dealerships%20but%20hasn't%20had%20much%20luck.%20She's%20hoping%20to%20find%20a%20job%20to%20supplement%20her%20%242%2C100%20monthly%20Social%20Security%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20live%20paycheck%20to%20paycheck%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Levier%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20Tampa%20area.%20%26quot%3BNo%20savings%2C%20no%20stocks%2C%20or%20bonds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she's%20in%20need%20of%20additional%20income%2C%20Levier%20said%20working%20would%20also%20help%20her%20stay%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20sitting%20around%20just%20not%20doing%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20enjoy%20being%20out%20and%20about%20and%20learning%20things.%20It%20helps%20me%20stay%20young.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4b7c37d-95cf-4439-958e-cd9e12b7fcb1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20partly%20for%20the%20fun%20of%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20some%20older%20Americans%20who%20need%20work%20to%20supplement%20Social%20Security%20said%20financial%20stability%20and%20fulfillment%20are%20their%20main%20motivators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Dugan%2C%2080%2C%20said%20he%20isn't%20desperate%20for%20the%20wages%20he%20earns%20