%20control%20%E2%80%94%20may%20be%20particularly%20vulnerable%20if%20their%20AI%20is%20deceived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommanders%20can%20no%20longer%20rely%20on%20traditional%20methods%20of%20deception%20like%20hiding%20troop%20movements%20or%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20argue%20Mark%20Askew%20and%20Antonio%20Salinas%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmwi.westpoint.edu%2Ftimeless-lessons-from-cannae-to-d-day-operational-art-on-the-sensor-rich-battlefield-of-the-twenty-first-century%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eessay%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Modern%20War%20Institute%20at%20West%20Point.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20shaping%20perceptions%20in%20sensor-rich%20environments%20requires%20a%20shift%20in%20thinking%20%E2%80%94%20from%20concealing%20information%20to%20manipulating%20how%20the%20enemy%2C%20including%20AI%20systems%20and%20tools%2C%20interpret%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20commanders%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20fool%20enemy%20generals%20using%20misdirection%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-made-realistic-decoys-of-weapons-to-fake-out-russia-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecoy%20armies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20letting%20slip%20false%20war%20plans.%20Today%2C%20nations%20will%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bfeeding%20adversaries%20accurate%20if%20misleading%20data%20that%20can%20manipulate%20their%20interpretation%20of%20information%20and%20misdirect%20their%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20essay%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20to%20turn%20AI%20into%20an%20Achilles%20heel%20of%20an%20enemy%20commander%20and%20their%20staffs.%20This%20can%20be%20done%20by%20making%20%26quot%3Btheir%20AI%20systems%20ineffective%20and%20break%20their%20trust%20in%20those%20systems%20and%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20essay%20suggests.%20%26quot%3BCommanders%20can%20overwhelm%20AI%20systems%20with%20false%20signals%20and%20present%20them%20with%20unexpected%20or%20novel%20data%3B%20AI%20tools%20excel%20at%20pattern%20recognition%2C%20but%20struggle%20with%20understanding%20how%20new%20variables%20(outside%20of%20their%20training%20data)%20inform%20or%20change%20the%20context%20of%20a%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bslight%20changes%20in%20a%20drone's%20appearance%20might%20cause%20AI%20to%20misidentify%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Askew%20and%20Salinas%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20not%20likely%20to%20be%20thrown%20off%20by%20small%20or%20subtle%20tweaks%2C%20but%20AI%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20enemy%20intentions%20or%20target%20weapons%2C%20modern%20armies%20today%20rely%20on%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20sources%20ranging%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmies-need-their-own-drone-air-force-flown-by-specialists-study-says-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrones%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20satellites%2C%20to%20infantry%20patrols%20and%20intercepted%20radio%20signals.%20The%20information%20is%20so%20copious%20that%20human%20analysts%20are%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20US%20Army's%2038th%20Infantry%20Division%20set%20up%20this%20command%20post%20for%20a%202023%20exercise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68028a93c6ad288d147e94d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Army's%2038th%20Infantry%20Division%20set%20up%20this%20command%20post%20for%20a%202023%20exercise.%3Cp%3EMaster%20Sgt.%20Jeff%20Lowry%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20AI%20so%20attractive%20is%20its%20speed%20at%20analyzing%20huge%20quantities%20of%20data.%20This%20has%20been%20a%20boon%20for%20companies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-coming-military-new-scaleai-contract-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScale%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20won%20lucrative%20Pentagon%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20power%20of%20AI%20also%20magnifies%20the%20damage%20it%20can%20do.%20%26quot%3BAI%20can%20coordinate%20and%20implement%20flawed%20responses%20much%20faster%20than%20humans%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Askew%20and%20Salinas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFooling%20AI%20can%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bmisallocation%20of%20enemy%20resources%2C%20delayed%20responses%2C%20or%20even%20friendly%20fire%20incidents%20if%20the%20AI%20misidentifies%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20By%20feeding%20false%20data%2C%20one%20can%20manipulate%20the%20enemy's%20perception%20of%20the%20battlefield%2C%20creating%20opportunities%20for%20surprise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20China%20are%20already%20devoting%20great%20efforts%20to%20military%20AI.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Faerospace-defense%2Frussia-says-it-is-ramping-up-ai-powered-drone-deployments-ukraine-2024-10-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20drones%20and%20cyberwarfare%2C%20while%20the%20Chinese%20military%20is%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-deepseek-spying-china-nvidia-probed-chips-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20planning%20and%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20rigidity%20of%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20command%20structures%20makes%20any%20reliance%20on%20AI%20an%20opening.%20%26quot%3BIn%20such%20systems%2C%20decisions%20often%20rely%20heavily%20on%20top-down%20information%20flow%2C%20and%20if%20the%20AI%20at%20the%20top%20is%20fed%20deceptive%20data%2C%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20widespread%20misjudgments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20said.%20%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20centralized%20structures%20might%20lack%20the%20flexibility%20to%20quickly%20adapt%20or%20cross-verify%20information%2C%20making%20them%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20deception%20if%20they%20cannot%20protect%20their%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20false%20images%20are%20fed%20to%20an%20enemy's%20sensors%2C%20such%20as%20video%20cameras%2C%20to%20try%20to%20get%20the%20AI%20to%20rush%20to%20the%20wrong%20conclusion%2C%20further%20blinding%20the%20human%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20adversaries%20such%20as%20Iran%20and%20North%20Korea%20%E2%80%94%20will%20seek%20to%20exploit%20weaknesses%20in%20American%20AI.%20Thus%2C%20the%20US%20military%20must%20take%20precautions%2C%20such%20as%20protecting%20the%20data%20that%20feeds%20its%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20constant%20presence%20of%20drones%20in%20Ukraine%20shows%20that%20the%20sweeping%20maneuvers%20and%20surprise%20attacks%20of%20Napoleon%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-allied-defeat-at-kasserine-pass-taught-about-fighting-nazis-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERommel%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20becoming%20relics%20of%20the%20past.%20But%20as%20the%20MWI%20essay%20points%20out%2C%20surveillance%20can%20determine%20enemy%20strength%2C%20but%20not%20enemy%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20means%20deception%20must%20focus%20on%20shaping%20what%20the%20adversary%20thinks%20is%20happening%20rather%20than%20avoiding%20detection%20altogether%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20essay%20said.%20%26quot%3BBy%20crafting%20a%20believable%20deception%20narrative%20%E2%80%94%20through%20signals%2C%20false%20headquarters%2C%20and%20logistical%20misdirection%20%E2%80%94%20commanders%20can%20lead%20enemy%20AI%20and%20human%20decision-makers%20to%20make%20ineffective%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20scam%2C%20military%20deception%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20it%20reinforces%20what%20the%20enemy%20already%20believes.%20The%20essay%20points%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%