e%20to%20a%20degree%20that%20Hannibal%20could%20never%20have%20imagined.%20AI%20can%20sift%20through%20vast%20amounts%20of%20sensor%20data.%20But%20there%20still%20remains%20the%20fog%20of%20war.%20%26quot%3BAI%20will%20not%20eliminate%20war's%20chaos%2C%20deception%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20%E2%80%94%20it%20will%20only%20reshape%20how%20those%20factors%20manifest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20essay%20concluded.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20systems%20may%20provide%20episodic%20clarity%2C%20they%20will%20never%20offer%20a%20perfect%2C%20real-time%20understanding%20of%20intent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-change-military-deception-operations-mildec-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745046361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68028aa2a466d2b74ab397e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-change-military-deception-operations-mildec-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Successful%20military%20operations%20must%20now%20fool%20both%20human%20commanders%20and%20the%20AI%20that%20advises%20them.%20This%20creates%20an%20opening%2C%20two%20US%20Army%20officers%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.co