C%20school%20students%2C%20and%20conservation%20enthusiasts%2C%20anywhere%20between%2030%20to%2050%20people%2C%20come%20together%20for%20a%20unique%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20learning%20about%20and%20participating%20in%20the%20conservation%20of%20Olive%20Ridley%20turtles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20walk%20begins%20around%2011%3A30%20pm%20when%20the%20group%20assembles.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20volunteers%20follows%20up%20with%20the%20registered%20participants%2C%20ensuring%20that%20those%20who%20are%20genuinely%20interested%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20join%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raghuraman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20starts%20with%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20of%20a%20briefing%20session%2C%20during%20which%20the%20volunteers%20explain%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20walk%2C%20the%20need%20for%20conservation%2C%20and%20the%20threats%20these%20turtles%20face.%20%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20the%20crowd%2C%20we%20conduct%20the%20session%20in%20English%20or%20Tamil%2C%20sometimes%20even%20splitting%20batches%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghuraman%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGUl9LsS3Me%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGUl9LsS3Me%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3