dia.com%2F255707%2Fmumbai-imk-architect-pune-symbiosis-hospital-low-cost-passive-cooling-jaali-bricks-ecofriendly-sustainable-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20architectural%20firm%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhose%20expertise%20dates%20back%20to%201957%3B%20their%20projects%20dominate%20the%20Indian%20skyline%2C%20functionality%20and%20culture%20convening%20in%20each.%20But%2C%20from%2030%20March%202025%20onwards%20%E2%80%94%20the%20day%20the%20walkway%20was%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20%E2%80%94%20I%20will%20recognise%20Rahul%20as%20the%20man%20who%20gifted%20Mumbai%20a%20time%20portal%20into%20the%20past.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20architect%20unravels%20the%20art%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20barely%20a%20month%20since%20the%20Malabar%20nature%20trail%20gained%20a%20place%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20memory.%20But%20it%20hardly%20feels%20like%20a%20newcomer.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20the%20trail%20always%20existed%20and%20just%20needed%20to%20be%20uncovered.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20amble%20along%20the%20walkway%2C%20guided%20by%20its%20contours%20and%20dips.%20Rahul%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20relies%20on%20muscle%20memory%20to%20find%20his%20way.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20forged%20these%20very%20trails%20as%20a%20child%20when%20he%E2%80%99d%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412368%2Ftirthan-valley-himachal-pradesh-tourism-kudrat-boutique-homestay-sustainable-architecture-stone-house-wood-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexplore%20the%20forest%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20his%20pet%20dog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22w